Package com.g1.mychess.player.model

Enum Class CustomChessRank

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<CustomChessRank>
com.g1.mychess.player.model.CustomChessRank
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<CustomChessRank>, Constable
public enum CustomChessRank extends Enum<CustomChessRank>
Enum representing custom chess ranks based on rating ranges. Each rank has a title and a rating range, and the enum provides methods to retrieve the rank based on a rating.
